member.summary:
Helper class to record undo operations in a block with using keyword.

using(new UndoBlock(undo, obj, "Rename"))
{
    obj.Name = "super name";
}

member.example:
using(new UndoMultiBlock(undo, objs, "Rename objects"))
{
	foreach(var e in objs)
		e.Name = "super name";
}

members.member:

Return the first plugin using the provided name.

/// The plugin name.
The plugin, or null if not loaded.
